@startuml fig-project-presentation
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
title Project Presentation Structure (7-10 min)

card "1. Introduction (1 min)\nProject name, technologies, team" as intro #E3F2FD
card "2. Live Demo (4 min)\nClean start, setup, features, capture" as demo #C8E6C9
card "3. Architecture (2 min)\nComponents, data flow, design decisions" as arch #FFF3E0
card "4. Q&A Defence (3 min)\nTechnical questions, lessons learned" as qa #FCE4EC

intro -d-> demo
demo -d-> arch
arch -d-> qa

legend bottom
Checklist:
README complete
Demo tested on clean VM
Backup video recorded
PCAP files prepared
endlegend
@enduml
